<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/freezingheart" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6401769); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6401769&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200736" alt="Freezingheart" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6401769)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/freezingheart" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6401769); return false;">Freezingheart</a></span></p>
